    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_1",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene3",
        "message":"Come closer, $playername, and learn the truth of every road you have walked and every lie told about it."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_2",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene2",
        "message":"We know the names you forgot, the faces you left behind, and the fate waiting at your door."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_3",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene1",
        "message":"Stay, and we will sing you the ending of your story."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_4",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene3",
        "message":"No man has sailed past us unchanged, for knowledge always takes its price."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_5",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene2",
        "message":"Listen, and you will understand why your brother still feels farther away with every mile."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_6",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene1",
        "message":"Untie yourself, clever one - wisdom should never be heard from a distance."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_7",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene3",
        "message":"What you seek is not safety, but certainty, and we can give you that."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_8",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene2",
        "message":"You have outwitted monsters and men, but you have never dared to face the truth we sing."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_9",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene1",
        "message":"Hear us, and you will finally know which of your victories were earned, and which were merely spared."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_10",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene3",
        "message":"We sing not to trap you, Odysseus, but to show you what you have been running from."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_x",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene2",
        "message":"One day, the knots won't be tied tightly enough. Or the blocked ears won't be closed tightly enough.",
        "replies":[
            {
				"nextPhraseID":"ll2_sirene_x_10",
                "text":"N"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_x_10",
		"switchToNPC":"sirene1",
        "message":"We are hungry but patient."
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_key",
        "message":"End of journey. This is as far as we can go.",
        "replies":[
            {
				"nextPhraseID":"ll2_sirene_key_10",
                "text":"Hey, there is still so much to expore."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_key_10",
        "message":"See the rocky island over there? This is where the sirens live.",
        "replies":[
            {
				"nextPhraseID":"ll2_sirene_key_30",
                "text":"Sirens?"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_key_30",
        "message":"Dreadful creatures. They have lured many a brave crew to the rocks. The ships were wrecked there, and the crew was never seen again.",
        "replies":[
            {
				"nextPhraseID":"ll2_sirene_key_40",
                "text":"Hmm, then just ignore it and we'll drive by really quickly."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_key_40",
        "message":"Absolutely not. I will not sacrifice my ship and crew to the childish wish of a kid.",
        "replies":[
            {
				"nextPhraseID":"ll2_sirene_key_50",
                "text":"Let me think: If you didn't hear the sirens, everything would be OK, right?"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_key_50",
        "message":"Of course. But we can't cover our ears and steer a ship at the same time.",
        "replies":[
            {
				"nextPhraseID":"ll2_sirene_key_60",
                "text":"Look, I have earplugs here, take them and you can drive through here as often as you like without any problems.",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"inventoryRemove",
                        "requireID":"earplugs",
                        "value":5
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"ll2_sirene_key_60",
        "message":"Sounds like a plan. And you? How do you plan to stop yourself from simply jumping overboard?",
        "replies":[
            {
				"nextPhraseID":"ll2_sirene_key_70",
                "text":"I'll take ear plugs too, of course."
            },
            {
				"nextPhraseID":"ll2_sirene_key_80",
                "text":"Just tie me to the mast. And whatever you do, don't untie me, no matter how much I beg."
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
